{"word":"G931 - βάσανος - básanos - bas'-an-os - Torment","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βάσανος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>básanos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>bas'-an-os"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Torment"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வேதனை - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"the touchstone, torture, torment, acute pains"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Perhaps remotely from the same as <a href=\"#/G939 - βάσις - básis - bas'-ece/939\">G939</a> (through the notion of <i>going</i> to the bottom); a <i>touch stone</i>, that is, (by analogy) <i>torture:</i> - torment."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G928 - βασανίζω - basanízō - bas-an-id'-zo/928\">G928</a>, <a href=\"#/G929 - βασανισμός - basanismós - bas-an-is-mos'/929\">G929</a>, <a href=\"#/G930 - βασανιστής - basanistḗs - bas-an-is-tace'/930\">G930</a>, <a href=\"#/G931 - βάσανος - básanos - bas'-an-os/931\">G931</a>"}]}